task.summary: Apiary delete et al, WeatherHistory future date ignorance, make foreign keys work.
Proper Reminder dealings done, update DAOs that have apiary & hive foreign keys to deal w/ the fact that there will only be a relation to 1 of them. GO CUBBIES!!! YOU DID IT!!!
More data objects and start Dialog. Work in progress.
MultiSelectOtherDialog fix from stackoverflow (thanks Anchal Singh). Tweaking necessary. MultiSelectOtherDialogNoAdapter initial test.
Dialog DB updates & retrieves working barebones w/ 1 data element set.
LogEntryList fix to externalize list values and make sure they do not repeat. 1st new buttons to launch value selection dialogs.
Dialog stuff. Mostly getting reminder item to appear properly.
Added another Dialog to HiveHealth. DOAs that have FKs for Hive & Apiary need to have the one not used nullified on update.
EditTextDialog fixing and and Dialog cancelling.
Concrete-ify setDialogDataCancel() in LogFragment so empty method need not be implemented in subclasses that don't need it.
More switch work from Dialog (DialogFragment) to true Fragment.
Numeric entry for EditText in DataEntry classes and some renaming.
More Dialog superclassing. Finished? Bug fixes.
Get rid of unused imports and other cleanup.
Working in getting notification/event description to work.
GetReminderTimeTask overhall, EventListActivity time retrieve good, testing needed.
EventList Notification working but more testing esp descriptions.
EventList Notification working better, maybe done.
GraphSelection almost done. Need to setup hand off.
Geocode final tweaks. Works on phone, not on emulator.
